USERS
------------------------
guest:
- read blog
- search blogs
- log-in (or register if not registered yet)

users(logged-in):
- same as guests

- comment

author(logged-in + registered):
- same as user

- log-out
- edit userdata
- post new blog

PAGES
--------------------

all pages:
- Header
- Sidebar
- Central part
______________

Header:
- Log-in
- Sign-in
- Update user profile
- Search

Sidebar:
- Users connected
- Total visitors
______________

Blogcentral (central part):
- Sorting function
- Show first six posts
- Function show more

Bloghome (central part):
- Unique URL (based on author)
- Short profile author
- All blogs author
- Sorting-function blogs
- Create new blog

Blogpost-detail-page (central part):
- Unique URL (based on author + post)
- Link to Bloghome author
- Complete post (blog + comments)
- Like button

